document_data.name: Jaqalwar Lansena
document_data.mainbody: '''Jaqalwar Lansena''' was one of the Merchant-Lords of [[Imdolphyn]] as of [[1479 DR]].{{Cite organized play/LFR/Quench the Fire of the Raging God|15}}
document_data.Activities: Jaqalwar was a well known playboy sailor, who owned a substantial trading fleet. He was also known for his preference to dally with women of exotic races, such as [[elves]], [[drow]] or [[genasi]].
